    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Let’s assume we need to land a rover on the surface of Mars. But we are interested in a specific area. Unfortunately for our rover, the chosen terrain is pretty hard to land on and that’s why we need deep learning.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">With a computer vision system (some sort of deep learning algorithm with Convolutional layers — CNNs), the rover can automatically find a safe place to land and do it in real-time while getting closer to the land. Remember, Mars is far away from Earth, so even light (signal) needs time to get there. We are talking about 3 minutes of light travel. That’s why we need rover to be independent.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">What is remarkable, this system <a href="https://www.ri.cmu.edu/cmu-robotics-alum-leads-development-of-critical-landing-technology-computer-vision-system-will-enable-safe-martian-landing-for-nasas-perseverance-rover/" target="_self">has already been used</a> by NASA, at least while landing Perseverance (2021).</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-5">Searching for minerals and water</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
