    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Maybe someday we will want to move heavy manufacturing to the Moon so our environment is safe. In that case, we need as much smart automation as possible, as we don’t want to leave a lot of people there. It’s a wide sphere, but computer vision would have a ton of applications here. Here are some use cases for computer vision in factories:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Quality control — detect anomalies, and defects;</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Autonomous robots move stuff and do other things humans do;</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Counting stuff;</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Safety (for example — fire detection)</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
