    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">When we are going to be far away from Earth on a mission, maybe on the Moon or Mars, we can’t take every specialist on board. That’s why automation is important also in healthcare. With some equipment and AI assistance, we can diagnose a wide variety of diseases.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We can already do a lot of things in healthcare with computer vision today. Here are a just couple of examples:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><ul><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Broken bones, bone loss, and other bone pathologies;</li><li class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Kidney stones, different types of cancer, and other soft tissue pathologies.</li></ul></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Moreover, we can use symptoms and other data to try to diagnose other (non-visual) diseases and to generate a treatment. What is more interesting, we can potentially mimic a real doctor’s visit. We can analyze video data, audio data, and symptoms to create a better understanding of the problem. Finally, we can work with mental health, too, analyzing speech and/or behavior.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
